    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/000",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The GNPS network from the 51 spectra was rebuilt... This network contains two large connected components of respective size 21 and 11, two pairs, and 15 spectra remaining isolated. The main components to be explained (disjoint cliques of size above 3, as well as pairs with similarity above 0.9) were extracted (findGNPSComponents method), leading to 5 disjoint cliques, in addition to the initial 4 connected components of the network. Finally, mineMS2 patterns of highest recall for these components were selected (findPatternsExplainingComponents method), with the precision and size of the patterns being used to split ties (see the package vignette): patterns explaining each component were found, with a minimum recall of 0.9 and a mean F1-score of 0.89 (minimum of 0.55).",
      "asbval:note": "The paper describes the general workflow of findPatternsExplainingComponents applied to P. nordicum network components, but does NOT provide specific details about 'component 8' with precursor m/z values 370.1283 and 404.0891, nor does it name a specific pattern 'P70' or report its F1-score as 1.0. The paper reports mean F1-score of 0.89 (minimum 0.55) across all components, not component-specific metrics. The specific component and pattern identifiers appear to be fabricated or from supplementary materials not provided in the passages.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-s13321-025-01051-y",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "partial",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_001",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "asbval:target_claim_field": "research_question",
      "asbval:target_claim_text": "When findPatternsExplainingComponents is applied to component 8 (a high-similarity pair of spectra with precursor m/z values 370.1283 and 404.0891) using recall-precision-size metrics and top=5, does pattern P70 achieve perfect F1-score while other top-5 patterns maintain recall=",
      "eco:evidence_type": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/ECO_0000361"
      },
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T13:51:58.634062+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_001/001",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "No such table or data frame is provided in the passages. The paper reports aggregate statistics (mean F1-score 0.89, minimum 0.55) but not per-component breakdowns with specific pattern identifiers like 'P70' or component numbers like '8'.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-s13321-025-01051-y",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "no",
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_001",
