      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/fragmentation-pattern-extraction-and-ranking/009",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "In molecular networks, as generated by the GNPS platform [27], each vertex is a spectrum and an edge indicates a high pairwise similarity according to the modified cosine score... The coupling of mineMS2 to molecular networks such as those generated by GNPS was therefore included as a feature of the mineMS2 software",
      "asbval:note": "GNPS is confirmed as the molecular networking platform used with mineMS2.",
