      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": null,
      "asbval:note": "igraph is not mentioned anywhere in the provided passages. The paper states mineMS2 is an R package that performs these operations, but does not name igraph as the underlying library used for graph parsing or component extraction.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1186-s13321-025-01051-y",
